---
description: Enforce maximum file size of 300 lines
globs: "**/*.{ts,tsx,py,js,jsx}"
alwaysApply: false
---

Maximum 300 lines per file. If a file exceeds this, split it into focused modules.

- Components, hooks, services, and utils should each be their own file.
- Functions maximum 50 lines. Extract helpers if longer.
- Prefer many small files over few large ones — makes parallel editing viable and reduces merge conflicts.
